AI response For Prompt what is mobile what is mobile
 ****************************************************************

 computing

Mobile computing refers to the use of portable electronic devices such as smartphones, laptops, tablets, and wearables to access information and perform various tasks while on the go. It encompasses the technology, hardware, and software required to enable this mobility and connectivity. Mobile computing allows users to access the internet, send and receive emails, make calls, access applications, and perform other functions from any location with a wireless connection. It has revolutionized the way people communicate, work, and access information, making it an integral part of modern life.